Classes

HTMLReader

Extract the significant text from an arbitrary HTML document. The contents of any head, script, style,
and xml tags are removed completely. The URLs for a[href] tags are extracted, along with the inner text
of the tag. All other tags are removed, and the inner text is kept intact. Html entities (e.g., &) are
not decoded.

