Classes

HuggingFaceEmbedding

Uses feature extraction from '@xenova/transformers' to generate embeddings. Per default the model
XENOVA_ALL_MINILM_L6_V2 is used.

Can be changed by setting the  modelType  parameter in the constructor, e.g.:

 

```typescript
new HuggingFaceEmbedding({
    modelType: HuggingFaceEmbeddingModelType.XENOVA_ALL_MPNET_BASE_V2,
});
```

<L=1f#2>Extends</L> <I=2>
-    BaseEmbedding 

