<L=46#I>indexMapping()?</L> <I=I>
   optional  indexMapping : (  enrichedDoc  ,  metadata  ) =>  T 

(Optional) function used to map document fields to the AI search index fields If none is specified a
default mapping is provided which uses the field keys. The keys in the enriched document are:
 ["id", "chunk", "embedding", "metadata"]  .

The default mapping is:

-    "id"  to idFieldKey
-    "chunk"  to chunkFieldKey
-    "embedding"  to embeddingFieldKey
-    "metadata"  to metadataFieldKey

