What is LlamaIndex.TS

LlamaIndex is the leading data framework for building LLM applications

LlamaIndex is a framework for building context-augmented generative AI applications with LLMs including
agents and workflows.

The TypeScript implementation is designed for JavaScript server side applications using  Node.js, 
Deno,  Bun,  Cloudflare Workers, and more.

LlamaIndex.TS provides tools for beginners, advanced users, and everyone in between.

